// ── Common-mode action helpers ────────────────────────────────────────────────
// REC/PLY: recording→play; stopped/empty→record; playing→record/overdub.
// Saves a pre-overdub undo snapshot when entering record from an existing loop.
function common_recply_pair(idx) local(oidx orec newstate) (
