// ── Assignment SysEx — on-change emission ────────────────────────────────────
// Detects when any of the five MIDI assignments change and immediately emits
// an assignment snapshot without waiting for the next heartbeat.
// Tracks per-lane st_note* values for g_chan_selected so that both the global
// header-row tweakers AND the per-lane row tweakers trigger an update.
// draw_global_tweaker keeps per-lane values in sync with globals in common mode,
// so the behavior is identical when all lanes share the same assignments.
